name: Aubergine In Repose
description:
An Aubergine rests atop a velvety woven and tasselled cushion surrounded by pomegranates, clementines, cherry tomatoes of various colour and framed by Devil's Ivy and Spider plants. The scene is set atop an antique wooden serving cabinet against a brushed velvet and muslin backdrop.

This scene was set to playfully imitate the style, lighting and forms of traditional oil paintings, namely still life and portraits. 

2021. Nikon D3500, 55-200mm Lens. 

Dual lamp lighting with accompanying daylight.

Aubergine: Tribute
